description._content: ID: D40005-47 Title: The Political drama. [A series of caricatures.] Illustrator: "Grant, Charles Jameson (Charles Jameson Grant)" Provenance: [London] : Printed and published by G. Drake, 12, Houghton Street, Clare Market, [1834-1835.] Caption: 'The five plagues of the country'. Above each of the figures is written; I govern the people. I pray for the people. I legislate for the people. I fought for the people. I preserve the peace for all four. And above the devil on the extreme right is; And I’ll have all five.
